This year marks our 6th year of SUMMER IN THE CITY, kicking off Wednesday, June 1st! SITC is a weekly gathering during the summer months for 18 to 25 year olds in the city of Atlanta. This is a great place to connect with others, develop meaningful friendships and grow in your faith.

